subject: Skiing
Sports Injuries
lead_paragraph: Jean-Baptiste Grange, the 2009 world champion, who missed most of last season with a knee injury, defeated Andre Myhrer to win the season’s first World Cup slalom by 0.33 seconds in Levi, Finland.
